B39.F.summary: Bayn Group AB (publ) develops and markets sugar reduction solutions for the food and beverage companies in Sweden. The company offers EUREBA, a sweetened fiber; and NAVIA, a steviol glycoside in the form of powders or granules. It also provides services to sensory profile existing products, benchmark competing products, customize sweetened fibers for your application, produce your customized sweetened fibers, comply with regulations and laws, and document product sheets, safety sheets, etc. The company was formerly known as Bayn Europe AB (publ) and changed its name to Bayn Group AB (publ) in August 2020. The company was founded in 2009 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.

FRILL-B.ST.summary: Frill Holding AB (publ) operates as a functional foods company in Sweden, the United Kingdom, and the United States. The company manufactures, markets, and sells food products, as well as produces foods in the form of bars and sweets. Its products include Frill, a healthy snacks made from fruits, berries, and vegetables; and Add Ice Cream, a healthy ice cream that delivers functional benefits, such as proteins and vitamins. The company also offers olive oil, pasta, truffles, and chocolates under the Bacoccoli brand; and healthy and functional products based on honey, dietary fiber, algae, and oats under the Bezzt of Nature brand. Frill Holding AB (publ) was founded in 2014 and is headquartered in Uppsala, Sweden.
